    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 0</strong> Necromancy</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> undefined touch</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nChanneling the chill of the grave, make a melee spell attack against a target within reach. On a hit, the target takes 1d10 Necrotic damage, and it can't regain Hit Points|XPHB until the end of your next turn.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 1d10 when you reach levels 5 (2d10), 11 (3d10), and 17 (4d10).</p>",
